NK001(ka)035:0: bslab pa yongs su sbyong ba gzhi gsum gyi cho
NK001(ka)035:1: ga thar gling du bgrod pa'i gru chen zhes bya
NK001(ka)035:2: ba bzhugs so // na mahsarba dz+ny+aa ya /
NK001(ka)035:3: dge legs yon tan kun gyi gter //
NK001(ka)035:4: srid mtshor bying ba rnams kyi skyabs //
NK001(ka)035:5: kun mkhyen 'gro ba'i bla ma la //
NK001(ka)035:6: rtag tu dang bas phyag byas te //
NK001(ka)035:7: nyes brgya'i chu gter rab bsgal nas //
NK001(ka)035:8: thar pa'i gling du bgrod byed pa'i //
NK001(ka)035:9: bslab pa yongs sbyong gzhi gsum gyi //
NK001(ka)035:10: cho ga legs bshad gru chen bya //
NK001(ka)035:16: dus nges pa can dang 'brel ba mthun pa'i gso sbyong gi dbang du byas te //
NK001(ka)035:17: ga mar tshes grangs nges pa'i phyir skud pa la
NK001(ka)035:18: smyig ma'i thur ma bco lnga brgyus pa nyi ma
NK001(ka)035:19: re re zhing spo bas zla ba'i ming grangs ya
NK001(ka)035:20: drug gi mar ngo'i nyin zhag bco lnga pa dor
NK001(ka)035:21: zhing gzhan rnams ma chad par bgrang /
NK001(ka)035:22: gal te zla bshol yod tshe gang la bshol don
NK001(ka)035:23: pa'i zla ba de thub mi thub gang yin kyang
NK001(ka)035:24: rung ste / nyis brtsegs kyi phyi ma nyid thub par rtsis te bgrang tshul nges par byas la /
NK001(ka)035:25: dge bskos kyis de la brtags nas nyin re zhing dge 'dun la barjoda cing mdo bskul bar bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:26: . nas gso sbyong gi dus la babs pa na /
NK001(ka)035:28: gtsug lag khang sogs 'du ba'i gnas byi dor gyis dag par bya /
NK001(ka)035:29: dri gtsang khang gi dbus lta bu mdo 'don pa
NK001(ka)035:30: po'i gong du ston pa'i sku gzugs khri la spyan
NK001(ka)035:31: drangs pa'i spyan sngar mchod pa rgyas par bsham /
NK001(ka)035:32: gzhi bdag la dkar gtor gtsang ma dang /
NK001(ka)035:33: mdo 'don pa po'i seng khri sogs stan rung ba go rim bzhin du bsham /
NK001(ka)035:36: gso sbyong la gnas pa'i dge bsnyen gyis kyang rung ste /
NK001(ka)035:37: gan+di brdung ba'i gnas su song la /
NK001(ka)035:38: dkon mchog la phyag byas nas shang tsa lan gsum
NK001(ka)035:39: sngon du 'gro bas las kyi gan+di rgyud gcig dang
NK001(ka)035:46: gso sbyong snga ma 'das pa'i mtha' tshun chad kyi
NK001(ka)035:47: rang rgyud kyi ltung ba la so sor brtags te
NK001(ka)035:48: / ltung ba byung bar shes na bshags bsdam byin
NK001(ka)035:49: gyis brlabs pa gang la gang 'os kyis phyir bcos
NK001(ka)035:52: lhag ma'i sbom po yang ba dang /
NK001(ka)035:55: nyes byas kyi sde tshan las gang rung zhig shes na /
NK001(ka)035:56: .sa ltung ba nang mi mthun pa'i dge slong gcig gi drung du phyin te /
NK001(ka)035:59: tsog pur thal mo sbyar nas /
NK001(ka)035:60: tshe dang ldan pa dgongs su gsol /
NK001(ka)035:61: bdag dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba la ltung ba 'di lta bu 'di byung ste /
NK001(ka)035:62: . dag pa'i mtha' tshun chad nas bzung ste tshe
NK001(ka)035:63: dang ldan pa'i mdun du mthol lo zhes sogs 'og
NK001(ka)035:64: nas 'byung ba ltar lan gsum dang mthong sdom dri
NK001(ka)035:66: de bzhin du pham pa'i sbom po lci yang dang /
NK001(ka)035:67: lhag ma'i sbom po lci ba ni rim pa ltar dge slong drug dang /
NK001(ka)035:69: bzhi yan chad kyi mdun du bshags tshigs de kho nas bshags /
NK001(ka)035:70: gal te dogs pa dang yid gnyis za na dge
NK001(ka)035:71: slong sde snod 'dzin pa la dris te phyir bcos
NK001(ka)035:72: bya / dge 'dun lhag ma dang spang ltung ni
NK001(ka)035:73: gang zag khyad par can gyis bshags pas 'dag na'ng
NK001(ka)035:74: bya / / gzhan gyis chad las kyi sgo nas
NK001(ka)035:75: bshags dgos pa ma grub par las kyi kha skongs
NK001(ka)035:76: la 'dun ltung ba de thun mong pa min zhing
NK001(ka)035:77: bya / / / bshags pas kyang mi 'dag pas thun mong min pa'i byin barlaba bya dgos te /
NK001(ka)035:78: ltung ba mi mthun pa'i dge slong gi drung du gzhan sngar ltar las /
NK001(ka)035:80: ltung ba de tshe dang ldan pa'i mdun du byin gyis barlaba bo //
NK001(ka)035:81: .nga ltung ba sogs 'og nas 'byung ba ltar lan gsum bzlas la thabs legs bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:82: yang las gral du 'dug ma thag tu bran nam /
NK001(ka)035:83: yid gnyis za na drung na mo la byin gyis barlaba tshul sngar ltar dang /
NK001(ka)035:84: las byed pas ni sems kyis barlaba par bshad do //
NK001(ka)035:85: bsdam bya'i nyes byas rnams ni sngar byas la gnod
NK001(ka)035:86: 'gyod dang phyis mi nyams par bsrung zhing bsdam par
NK001(ka)035:88: . nas las de ma grub bar du nyes ltung gis ma gos par bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:89: . yang spyir chos 'di pa'i phyir bcos byed tshul ni /
NK001(ka)035:90: pham pa 'chab med la bslab byin gyis bcos /
NK001(ka)035:91: lhag ma 'chab bcas la spo mgu dbyung ba ster spang ltung dngos po spangs la bshags /
NK001(ka)035:92: sor bshags mtshams kyi phyi rol du smre sngags dang bcas pas bshags /
NK001(ka)035:93: ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa dang bshags bya'i nyes byas rnams rang rang gi ming gis bshags /
NK001(ka)035:95: bshag yul ma rnyed na byin gyis barlaba pa ste /
NK001(ka)035:96: rang rang gi cho gas bcos dgos pa nyid do //
NK001(ka)035:97: . lta na'ng ltung ba'i ming rigs so sor 'byed
NK001(ka)035:98: mi nus pa sogs kyis de rnams ji bzhin pa
NK001(ka)035:99: ma grub pas / .sa sang gi phyag len ltar
NK001(ka)035:100: gnas khang gcig tu 'dus nas phan tshun barjoda res
NK001(ka)035:101: kyis thams cad dge 'dun las bshags na /
NK001(ka)035:102: 'os pa'i phyag dang 'dug tshul sngar lta bus /
NK001(ka)035:103: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol /
NK001(ka)035:104: bdag dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba byis pa nyid dang /
NK001(ka)035:108: nyon mongs pa mang ba'i dbang gis /
NK001(ka)035:109: pham lhag gi sbom po lci yang gnyis dang /
NK001(ka)035:111: so sor bshags par bya ba dang /
NK001(ka)035:112: nyes byas kyi sde tshan rnams las kha na ma
NK001(ka)035:113: tho ba gang dang gang byung ba de dang de
NK001(ka)035:114: dag pa'i mtha' tshun chad nas bzung ste /
NK001(ka)035:115: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams kyi mdun du mthol lo //
NK001(ka)035:117: mthol zhing bshags na bde ba la reg par gnas par 'gyur gyi /
NK001(ka)035:118: ma mthol ma bshags na ni mi 'gyur ro //
NK001(ka)035:120: nyes ltung de dag la nyes ltung de dag tu gzigs lags sam zhes dri /
NK001(ka)035:122: len pa pos phyin chad legs par sdom lags sam /
NK001(ka)035:125: de bzhin du byin rlabs la'ng dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol /
NK001(ka)035:126: bdag dge slong sogs nas nyon mongs pa mang ba'i dbang gis /
NK001(ka)035:127: dge 'dun lhag ma'i chos bcu gsum dang /
NK001(ka)035:128: spang ltung sum cu las gang yang rung ba byung ba de /
NK001(ka)035:129: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams kyi mdun du byin gyis barlaba bo //
NK001(ka)035:130: .nga ltung ba de byin gyis brlabs te dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong mdzad la /
NK001(ka)035:131: slad kyis ltung ba de chos bzhin du slar bagyi'o //
NK001(ka)035:132: zhes lan gsum bzlas la thabs legs bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:133: . ltar rgyud dag par byas nas gso sbyong gi
NK001(ka)035:134: gnas der dge 'dun thams cad tshogs te mchil lhwam
NK001(ka)035:135: phud cing gral la 'khod pa na /
NK001(ka)035:137: thal sbyar 'dud pa dang bcas te /
NK001(ka)035:138: bstan pa rin po che'i rtsa lag dam par gyur pa mkhan po'am /
NK001(ka)035:140: gnas brtan pa'i zhal snga nas gtso mdzad dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:141: .nga zla ba yar gyi ngo'i gral tshes bco lnga pa'am /
NK001(ka)035:142: mar gyi ngo'i bcu bzhi pa'am bco lnga mngon du gyur pa lags te /
NK001(ka)035:143: gtsug lag khang gi bdag po dang gtsug lag khang
NK001(ka)035:144: gi lha rnams kyi slad du zhal nas gsungs pa'i
NK001(ka)035:145: tshigs su bcad pa de klog tu gsol /
NK001(ka)035:146: zhes bskul bas dge 'dun rnams bzhengs /
NK001(ka)035:147: snam sbyar gyon nas rgyud cha gsum pa 'don par bya ste /
NK001(ka)035:148: de la thog mar phyag 'tshal ba'i rgyud ni /
NK001(ka)035:149: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK001(ka)035:150: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rig pa dang
NK001(ka)035:154: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba /
NK001(ka)035:156: lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa mnyam med sh+aakya'i
NK001(ka)035:157: rgyal po'i zhabs kyi rdul dri ma med pa la
NK001(ka)035:158: mgo bos rab tu gtugs te gus pas phyag 'tshal
NK001(ka)035:159: lo // gang tshe rkang gnyis gtso bo khyod bltams tshe //
NK001(ka)035:160: sa chen 'di la gom pa bdun bor nas //
NK001(ka)035:161: nga ni 'jig rten 'di na mchog ces gsungs //
NK001(ka)035:162: . tshe mkhas pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK001(ka)035:163: rnam dag sku mnga' mchog tu gzugs bzang ba //
NK001(ka)035:164: ye shes rgya mtsho gser gyi lhun po 'dra //
NK001(ka)035:165: grags pa 'jig rten gsum na lhang nge ba //
NK001(ka)035:166: mgon po mchog brnyes khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK001(ka)035:167: mtshan mchog ldan pa dri med zla ba'i zhal //
NK001(ka)035:168: gser mdog 'dra ba khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK001(ka)035:169: rdul bral khyod 'dra srid pa gsum ma mchis //
NK001(ka)035:170: mnyam med mkhyen can khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK001(ka)035:171: mgon po thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK001(ka)035:172: thams cad mkhyen pa ston pa po //
NK001(ka)035:173: bsod nams yon tan rgya mtsho'i gzhi //
NK001(ka)035:174: de bzhin gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK001(ka)035:175: dag pa 'dod chags bral ba'i rgyu //
NK001(ka)035:176: dge bas ngan song las grol zhing //
NK001(ka)035:177: gcig tu don dam mchog gyur pa //
NK001(ka)035:178: zhi gyur chos la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK001(ka)035:179: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK001(ka)035:180: bslab pa dag la rab tu gus //
NK001(ka)035:181: zhing gi dam pa yon tan zhing //
NK001(ka)035:185: ji snyed su dag ces sogs kyi yan lag bdun pa'ng bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:186: . nas mdo gdon pa'i rgyun ni /
NK001(ka)035:187: shes rab snying po lta bu zhig gi mjug tu /
NK001(ka)035:189: {ra ma rab rib mar me dang //
NK001(ka)035:190: sgyu ma zil pa chu bur dang //
NK001(ka)035:191: rmi lam glog dang sprin lta bu //
NK001(ka)035:192: 'dus byas chos rnams de ltar lta //
NK001(ka)035:193: chos rnams thams cad rgyu las byung //
NK001(ka)035:195: rgyu la 'gog pa gang yin pa //
NK001(ka)035:196: dge sbyong chen pos 'di skad gsung //
NK001(ka)035:197: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK001(ka)035:198: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spya. //
NK001(ka)035:199: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul //
NK001(ka)035:200: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK001(ka)035:201: . nas bsngo ba'i rgyud rnams ni /
NK001(ka)035:202: bsod nams 'di yis thams cad gzigs pa nyid ///
NK001(ka)035:203: ba nas nyes pa'i dgra rnams pham byas te //
NK001(ka)035:204: skye rga na 'chi'i rba klong 'khrug pa yi //
NK001(ka)035:205: srid pa'i mtsho las 'gro ba sgrol bar shog /
NK001(ka)035:206: 'gro ba'i sdug basngala sman gcig pu //
NK001(ka)035:207: bde ba thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK001(ka)035:208: bstan pa rnyed dang bkur sti dang //
NK001(ka)035:209: bcas te- yun ring gnas gyur cig /
NK001(ka)035:210: klu rgyal dga' bo nyer dga' bo //
NK001(ka)035:211: gzhan yang grong khyer gnas pa rnams //
NK001(ka)035:212: tshe ring nad med phun sum tshogs //
NK001(ka)035:213: rtag tu bde ba thob par shog /
NK001(ka)035:215: . nas gtor ma btang ba ni /
NK001(ka)035:217: rang rang gi spyod yul du gyur pa'i gtor snod
NK001(ka)035:218: kyi nang du gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya'i skye
NK001(ka)035:219: mched kyi ngo bor gyur pa'i bza' btung 'dod pa'i
NK001(ka)035:220: yon tan du mas gang bar gyur /
NK001(ka)035:221: a k+aa ro mu kham sarba d+ha r+m+aa n+aam +aad+ya nut+pan+na tot+te +aahh+aum phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK001(ka)035:222: zhes lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK001(ka)035:223: gnyug mar gnas pa'i lha mo 'phrog ma la sogs pa gnas dang gzhi'i bdag po dang /
NK001(ka)035:227: ngam grog la sogs par 'khod pa'i 'byung po gtor
NK001(ka)035:228: ma za bar 'dod pa rnams kyi zhal du ba
NK001(ka)035:229: lim ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK001(ka)035:231: 'jig rten bde zhing lo legs dang //
NK001(ka)035:233: dge legs thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK001(ka)035:236: . nas dge bskos kyis spyod lam sngar ltar 'greng ste /
NK001(ka)035:237: bstan pa rin po che'i rtsa lag dam par gyur pa mkhan po'am /
NK001(ka)035:239: gnas brtan ming 'di zhes bgyi ba gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:240: .nga dus bzang po la bdag cag 'dir 'dus shing
NK001(ka)035:241: tshogs pa rnams la thugs brtse bas nye bar dgongs
NK001(ka)035:242: te ston pa'i bka'i chos nyan pa sbyin du gsol
NK001(ka)035:246: mdo 'don pa po khri 'dzegs te 'di skad ces /
NK001(ka)035:247: . yang slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa'i zhal nas /
NK001(ka)035:248: dge ba mtha' dag yang dag gso byed cing //
NK001(ka)035:249: sdig pa mtha' dag yang dag 'dir sbyong ba //
NK001(ka)035:250: dge gso phyir dang sdig pa rnams sbyong phyir //
NK001(ka)035:251: de bzhin gsheg pas gso sbyong zhes gsungs so //
NK001(ka)035:252: zhes pas gnyen pos bslab pa gso zhing /
NK001(ka)035:253: spang bya sdig pa sbyong bas na gso sbyong zhes bya /
NK001(ka)035:254: gso sbyong la'ng zhi gnas kyi gso sbyong dang /
NK001(ka)035:255: mthun pa'i gso sbyong gnyis las 'dir phyi ma /
NK001(ka)035:256: de la'ng dus nges can dang /
NK001(ka)035:257: dus ma nges par bya ba gnyis las /
NK001(ka)035:258: 'dir bcom ldan 'das kyis gso sbyong bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:259: zla ba phyed phyed kyi tshes bco lnga la'o //
NK001(ka)035:260: zhes gsungs pa ltar phyag len du bgyid pa la /
NK001(ka)035:262: sbyor ba la'ng gan+di brdung ba /
NK001(ka)035:264: dris pa'i tshig gis lan gdab pa /
NK001(ka)035:265: stan stabs mi nyams par bya ba rnams sngon du song nas /
NK001(ka)035:266: chos 'chad nyan nyams su myong ba chos sgrags kyi mdo dang /
NK001(ka)035:267: dus bzang gi mdo'i dod tshul khrims yang dag par
NK001(ka)035:268: ldan pa'i mdo la mdzad pa phyag len du gda'
NK001(ka)035:270: gang zhig gser mchog rang bzhin ri rab la gnas man+d+ha ra dang lhar bcas gnod sbyin dang /
NK001(ka)035:271: gdengs ka nor bu'i 'od kyis mun pa sel mdzad sa 'og gnas pa'i klu rnams gang yin dang /
NK001(ka)035:272: gangs can rir ni dpal gyis rol zhing rab tu dga' ba'i rig pa 'dzin pa gang yin pa /
NK001(ka)035:273: . dag thams cad thar pa dam pa'i sgor gyur thub pa'i gsung mnyan phyir ni 'dir gshegs shig /
NK001(ka)035:274: lha dang lha min mi dang mi'am ci yi dbang po dang //
NK001(ka)035:275: brgya byin la sogs chos kyi phyogs la bya ba byas pa rnams //
NK001(ka)035:276: sangs rgyas gsung rab rab tu zhi zhing bde ba'i rgyur gyur pa //
NK001(ka)035:277: 'di dag bshad kyis dam pa'i chos mnyan phyir ni 'dir gshegs shig /
NK001(ka)035:278: gang dag phyogs bcu stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK001(ka)035:279: bde gshegs slob mar gyur pa gang su dag /
NK001(ka)035:280: .nga 'dir ston pas chos kyi char 'bebs kyi //
NK001(ka)035:281: nyan par 'dod pa thams cad 'dir gshegs shig /
NK001(ka)035:283: sh+ai la sam yuk+ta s+au tra /
NK001(ka)035:285: tshul khrims yang dag par ldan pa'i mdo /
NK001(ka)035:286: thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK001(ka)035:287: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK001(ka)035:288: bcom ldan 'das mnyan yod na rgyal bu rgyal byed
NK001(ka)035:289: kyi tshal mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra
NK001(ka)035:290: ba na dge slong brgya phrag phyed dang bcu gsum
NK001(ka)035:291: gyi dge slong gi dge 'dun chen po dang thabs
NK001(ka)035:293: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong rnams la bka' stsal pa /
NK001(ka)035:297: ston pa'i bstan pa yang nges par 'jig par 'gyur na /
NK001(ka)035:298: ci'i phyir brtson 'grus dang brtul ba brtan pos sgrub par mi bye. /
NK001(ka)035:299: mi'i lus ni shin tu rnyed par dka' ba /
NK001(ka)035:300: . thob nas des rnyed pa'i rgyal ba'i bstan pa
NK001(ka)035:301: la rab tu byung ba yang rnyed nas thar pa'i
NK001(ka)035:302: don dang mi mthun pa dag gis bslus te sdug
NK001(ka)035:304: dge slong dag srog dang bral zhing shi ba ni sla'i /
NK001(ka)035:305: tshul khrims nyams shing zhigs pa ni de lta ma yin no //
NK001(ka)035:307: srog dang bral zhing shi bas ni tshe 'di nyid kyi skye ba zad par 'gyur gyi /
NK001(ka)035:308: tshul khrims nyams shing zhig pas ni skye ba 'bum
NK001(ka)035:309: phrag brgya'i bar du rigs dang bral zhing bde ba
NK001(ka)035:310: spang te rnam par ltung ba chen po nyams su
NK001(ka)035:312: . phyir ston pas tshul khrims rab basngagasa shing //
NK001(ka)035:313: tshul khrims ldan pa sangs rgyas 'byung ba 'phrad //
NK001(ka)035:314: tshul khrims ldan pa rgyan rnams kun gyi mchog /
NK001(ka)035:315: tshul khrims ldan pa dri dang byug pa yin //
NK001(ka)035:316: tshul khrims ldan pa dga' ba kun gyi gnas //
NK001(ka)035:317: tshul khrims ldan pa gdung ba bsil ba'i chu //
NK001(ka)035:318: tshul khrims ldan pa 'jig rten kun gyis bsto. //
NK001(ka)035:319: tshul khrims dag gis 'gro ba dam pa mnos //
NK001(ka)035:320: ji ltar sbrul gdug klu chen nag po yang //
NK001(ka)035:321: tshul khrims ldan la gnod med gzhan ci smos //
NK001(ka)035:322: tshul khrims ldan pa'i dge slong 'od dang ldan //
NK001(ka)035:323: tshul khrims ldan pa grags 'gyur bde ba thob //
NK001(ka)035:324: ji ltar mig med gzugs mthong mi rung ltar //
NK001(ka)035:325: de bzhin tshul khrims med na chos mi- mthong //
NK001(ka)035:326: ji ltar rkang med lam 'jug ga la nus //
NK001(ka)035:327: de bzhin tshul khrims med na thar mi 'gyur //
NK001(ka)035:328: ji ltar bum pa bzang po rin chen sno. //
NK001(ka)035:329: de bzhin tshul khrims chos rnams skyed pa'i gzhi //
NK001(ka)035:330: ji ltar bum chag rin chen snod mi rung //
NK001(ka)035:331: de bzhin tshul khrims ral pas chos kun gtugs //
NK001(ka)035:332: dang po tshul khrims med par gyur pa de //
NK001(ka)035:333: phyi nas mya ngan 'das pa thob snyam mam //
NK001(ka)035:334: sna med sna rdum la sogs gang yin pa //
NK001(ka)035:335: de la me long dag ni dgos mi 'gyur //
NK001(ka)035:336: rna bas ma thos mig sngar ma mthong yang //
NK001(ka)035:337: bstan bsrung mi de mtho ris 'gro bar 'gyur ///
NK001(ka)035:338: sa mang thos ldan thos bsrung mtho ris nyid //
NK001(ka)035:339: bud med bsten du ga la rung //
NK001(ka)035:340: rgyal po'i pho brang ga la dga' //
NK001(ka)035:341: longs spyod rtag pa ga la yo. //
NK001(ka)035:342: .bu ba snying po ga la yo. //
NK001(ka)035:343: bud med dag la rung ba med //
NK001(ka)035:344: rgyal srid dag la dga' ba med //
NK001(ka)035:345: lbu ba dag la snying po med //
NK001(ka)035:346: longs spyod dag la snying po med //
NK001(ka)035:347: longs spyod dag ni 'bab chu bzhin //
NK001(ka)035:349: me tog ci 'dra gzugs de bzhin //
NK001(ka)035:350: srog ni chu bur 'dra ba yin //
NK001(ka)035:351: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas
NK001(ka)035:352: nye bar 'khor la sogs pa'i dge slong de dag
NK001(ka)035:353: yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la
NK001(ka)035:356: chos bshad pa las byung ba yi //
NK001(ka)035:357: dge ba grub pa gang yod pa //
NK001(ka)035:359: srid pa'i mtsho las sgrol bar shog /
NK001(ka)035:361: . nas skabs 'dir dge tshul gyi gso sbyong mdzad pa ni /
NK001(ka)035:362: mdo dang karma sha tam du ma bshad kyang /
NK001(ka)035:364: gal te mngon sum gsungs pa med gyur kyang //
NK001(ka)035:365: dgag dbye gsungs phyir 'dir ni gso sbyong yo. //
NK001(ka)035:367: . yang rgyud nyes byas kyis ma gos na des chog /
NK001(ka)035:368: gal te gos na de bshags te gso sbyong bya dgos pas //
NK001(ka)035:369: ga mar nyes ba de byung ma thag tu dge
NK001(ka)035:370: slong gang yang rung ba zhig gi drung du song
NK001(ka)035:371: ste bshags / . ltar ma grub na 'dir dge
NK001(ka)035:372: 'dun gyi nang du dge slong zhig gi mdun du
NK001(ka)035:373: bshags na'ng rung bas phyag byas /
NK001(ka)035:377: tshe dang ldan pa dgongs su gsol /
NK001(ka)035:378: bdag dge tshul ming 'di zhes bgyi ba la 'di lta bu'i nyes byas 'di byung ste /
NK001(ka)035:379: zhes sam de ltar mi nus na /
NK001(ka)035:380: bdag dge tshul ming 'di zhes bgyi ba byis pa nyid dang /
NK001(ka)035:384: nyon mongs pa mang ba'i dbang gis nyes byas gang
NK001(ka)035:385: dang gang byung ba de dag pa'i mtha' tshun chad
NK001(ka)035:386: nas bzung ste / mkhan po'am nas /
NK001(ka)035:387: tshe dang ldan pa'i mdun du mthol lo 'chags so //
NK001(ka)035:388: mthol zhing bshags na bdag bde ba la reg par gnas par 'gyur gyi /
NK001(ka)035:389: ma mthol ma bshags na ni mi 'gyur ro //
NK001(ka)035:390: zhes lan gsum dang mthong sdom thabs legs bya /
NK001(ka)035:392: dge slong zhig gi mdun du phyag byas tsog pur 'dug ste /
NK001(ka)035:394: .nga dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'am bco lnga pa lags te /
NK001(ka)035:395: bdag dge tshul ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i yang gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'am bco lnga pa lags la /
NK001(ka)035:396: bdag dge tshul ming 'di zhes bgyi ba bar chad
NK001(ka)035:397: kyi chos rnams kyis yongs su dag go zhes bdag
NK001(ka)035:398: mchi na / bdag bar chad kyi chos rnams kyis
NK001(ka)035:399: yongs su dag par mkhan po sogs kyis gzung du
NK001(ka)035:400: mchi na / gsol // zhes lan gsum dang /
NK001(ka)035:402: sa pa'i nye- 'khor las logs su bkar ro //
NK001(ka)035:403: . nas dge slong gi gso sbyong ni /
NK001(ka)035:404: ltung ba thun mong ma yin pa phyir bcos dgos pa rnams gong du ma grub na 'dir bya /
NK001(ka)035:405: gal te ltung ba nang mthun pas bshags yul ma
NK001(ka)035:406: rnyed pa rnams ni thun mong gi byin barlaba bya
NK001(ka)035:407: ste / de'i sngags ni mdo 'don pa pos thog
NK001(ka)035:408: mar yul dus kyi stobs kyis bshags par ma nus
NK001(ka)035:409: pa'i ltung ba thun mong ba rnams kyis las la
NK001(ka)035:410: mi sgrib par bya ba'i phyir gsol ba'i las kyis
NK001(ka)035:411: byin gyis barlaba par bgyi bas dge 'dun rnams spyod
NK001(ka)035:412: lam bstun nas gsol ba'i las la thugs gtad par
NK001(ka)035:413: ste / zhu / dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:414: .nga dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'am bco lnga pa lags la /
NK001(ka)035:415: bdag cag dge 'dun thams cad ni ltung ba dang bcas par gyur na /
NK001(ka)035:416: gang gi mdun du bdag cag gi ltung ba de chos bzhin du slar bgyi ba /
NK001(ka)035:417: bdag cag las dge slong gnas gzhan du mchis la /
NK001(ka)035:418: dge slong gi mdun du ltung ba de dag chos
NK001(ka)035:419: bzhin du slar bgyid par spro ba su yang ma
NK001(ka)035:420: mchis na / gal te dge 'dun gyis dus la
NK001(ka)035:421: bab cing bzod na dge 'dun gyi gnang bar mdzod
NK001(ka)035:422: mchis na / cig dang / dge 'dun gyis deng
NK001(ka)035:423: ltung ba de byin gyis brlabs te gso sbyong mdzad
NK001(ka)035:424: mchis na / cig dang / la / slad kyis
NK001(ka)035:425: dge slong gi mdun du ltung ba de dag chos
NK001(ka)035:428: . nas sngar gnas la blo mthun byas pa zhig
NK001(ka)035:429: pa'am ma byas pa yin na 'di ltar bya ste
NK001(ka)035:430: / gnas pa blo mthun bgyi bas /
NK001(ka)035:431: las mdzad pa'i gnas 'di nye 'khor dang bcas pa
NK001(ka)035:432: tshun chad gso sbyong gi- gnas su blo bstun pa
NK001(ka)035:433: gsol ba'i las la thugs gtad par zhu /
NK001(ka)035:434: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:437: lags pa nang mtshams dang phyi rol nye 'khor 'dom
NK001(ka)035:438: gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong
NK001(ka)035:439: gi gnas su blo mthun par bzhed na /
NK001(ka)035:440: gal te dge 'dun gyi dus la bab cing bzod na /
NK001(ka)035:441: dge 'dun gyi gnang bar mdzod cig dang /
NK001(ka)035:442: dge 'dun gyi gnas thams cad grub pa'am /
NK001(ka)035:444: lags pa nang mtshams dang phyi rol nye 'khor 'dom
NK001(ka)035:445: gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong
NK001(ka)035:446: gi gnas su blo mthun par bagyi'o //
NK001(ka)035:448: barjoda pa mjug sdud dang bcas pa la thugs gtad par zhu /
NK001(ka)035:449: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:451: 'dom gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong gi gnas su bzhed de /
NK001(ka)035:454: 'dom gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong gi gnas su blo mthun par bgyi na /
NK001(ka)035:455: tshe dang ldan pa gang dag gnas thams cad nas /
NK001(ka)035:456: 'dom gang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong
NK001(ka)035:457: gi gnas su blo mthun par bgyi bar bzod pa
NK001(ka)035:458: de dag ni cang ma gsung zhig /
NK001(ka)035:459: gang dag mi bzod pa de- dag ni gsungs shig /
NK001(ka)035:460: dge 'dun gyis bzod cing gnang nas dge 'dun gyi gnas thams cad nas /
NK001(ka)035:461: 'dom gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyi gso
NK001(ka)035:462: sbyong gi gnas su blo mthun par bgyis lags te
NK001(ka)035:463: / 'di ltar cang mi gsung bas de de bzhin du 'dzin to //
NK001(ka)035:464: 'dir grub pa ni brag skyibs lta bu rang grub /
NK001(ka)035:465: bgyis pa ni skyes bu'i byed 'phro /
NK001(ka)035:466: lags pa ni byas nas zin pa ste skabs su gang bab barjoda do //
NK001(ka)035:467: . dag ni sbyor ba'i chos te /
NK001(ka)035:468: de las rgyud cha gsum 'don pa dang gtor ma
NK001(ka)035:469: btang ba ni nyin re zhing yang byar rung la
NK001(ka)035:470: / chos bshad nyan ni nya stong tshes brgyad kyi
NK001(ka)035:471: dus bzang po rnams kyi mtshan mo bya bar gsung
NK001(ka)035:472: pas gso sbyong gi snga phyi gang du byas kyang
NK001(ka)035:473: rung ba'i phyir med mi rung gi sbyor ba ma
NK001(ka)035:474: / yin na'ng / 'dir gso sbyong gi sngon du
NK001(ka)035:475: 'brel chags su mdzad pa'i phyag len ltar sbyar bas
NK001(ka)035:477: thun min gyi ltung ba bshags bsdams barlaba pa dang /
NK001(ka)035:478: thun mong ba gsol ba 'ba' zhig gis barlaba pa
NK001(ka)035:479: rnams ni ltung ba can dge 'dun gyi las la
NK001(ka)035:480: 'jug pa thams cad kyi sngon 'gror med mi rung
NK001(ka)035:481: gi yan lag tu snang bas gso sbyong gi'anga sbyor
NK001(ka)035:483: 'on kyang ltung bas ma gos pa'i gang zag khyad
NK001(ka)035:484: par can la mi dgos pas mtha' gcig tu nges
NK001(ka)035:485: par dgos pa'i sbyor bar mi 'gyur la /
NK001(ka)035:487: gnyug mar gnas pa'i dge 'dun gyi gtsug lag khang
NK001(ka)035:488: lta bu blo mthun ma zhig pa yin nam byas
NK001(ka)035:489: kyang chog / gzhan du na med mi rung gi sbyor bar 'gyur zhing /
NK001(ka)035:490: las kyi mtshams che chung gang rung gcod pa sogs ni 'dir btang snyoms su byas so //
NK001(ka)035:491: . nas gso sbyong gi gzhi dngos la /
NK001(ka)035:494: dang po ni mdo 'don cing nyan pa ste /
NK001(ka)035:496: so so thar pa la ston pa'i 'du shes /
NK001(ka)035:497: rang nyid kyi bslab pa la gces spras su byed pa'i 'du shes /
NK001(ka)035:498: tshul 'di la brten na rgyal ba'i bstan pa yun ring du gnas pa'i 'du shes te /
NK001(ka)035:499: . ltar thugs la bzhag nas gsan par zhu /
NK001(ka)035:501: mchod barjoda rnams kyi dus thal mo sbyor zhing /
NK001(ka)035:502: gzhan gyi tshe thal mo bsnol nas rab tu zhi ba'i tshul gyis /
NK001(ka)035:504: pra ti mo k+sha s+au tra /
NK001(ka)035:507: thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK001(ka)035:508: snyan pa'i ba dan 'jig rten gsum du grags //
NK001(ka)035:509: dam pa'i chos sgra sed+ge'i sgra bsgrags pas //
NK001(ka)035:510: thams cad mkhyen pa dkon cog mdzod bsnyes pa //
NK001(ka)035:511: zhabs la tshangs dbang gtsug gi nor bus gtugs //
NK001(ka)035:512: sdug basngala rgya mtsho gting mtha' med brgal ba //
NK001(ka)035:513: 'gro ba'i gtso la spyi bos phyag 'tshal te //
NK001(ka)035:514: thams cad mkhyen pa'i bslab gzhi dkon cog sno. //
NK001(ka)035:515: 'phags pa'i tshogs kyi dbus su dbye bar bya //
NK001(ka)035:516: sangs rgyas 'dul ba gangs can mtsho //
NK001(ka)035:517: gting mtha' med pa thams cad kyi //
NK001(ka)035:518: gnas pa'i snying dang snying po ni //
NK001(ka)035:519: so sor thar pa 'di yin no //
NK001(ka)035:520: 'di ni dam chos rgyal po yi //
NK001(ka)035:521: chos kun gyi ni 'dren pa mchog /
NK001(ka)035:522: 'di ni dge slong tshong tshogs kyi //
NK001(ka)035:523: bslab zong tshong khang chen po yin //
NK001(ka)035:524: tshul khrims 'chal bas zin rnams kyi //
NK001(ka)035:525: gdug pa rnams sel sman 'di yin //
NK001(ka)035:527: rkang gnyis gzhon nu'i lcags kyu yin //
NK001(ka)035:528: mtsho ba zab pa'i 'khor ba las //
NK001(ka)035:529: sgrol ba'i brgal thabs 'di yin te //
NK001(ka)035:531: nges pa'i chu lon zam pa yin //
NK001(ka)035:532: 'di ni nyon mongs pham byed lam //
NK001(ka)035:533: rgyal po yi ni 'dren pa mchog /
NK001(ka)035:535: ma skas gzhi dang 'dra bar gnas //
NK001(ka)035:536: nga ni mya ngan 'das gyur na //
NK001(ka)035:538: rang byung nyid kyis gus bcas par //
NK001(ka)035:539: nan tan dge slong tshogs 'dun bsto. //
NK001(ka)035:540: sangs rgyas zhes bya'i sgra 'di yang //
NK001(ka)035:541: 'jig rten dag na rab tu dkon //
NK001(ka)035:542: mi nyid rnyed pa shin tu dka' //
NK001(ka)035:543: rab tu byung ba shin tu dkon //
NK001(ka)035:544: de bzhin rab tu byung rnams kyi //
NK001(ka)035:545: tshul khrims phun sum tshogs rab dkon //
NK001(ka)035:546: tshul khrims yongs su dag gyur kyang //
NK001(ka)035:547: grogs bzang shin tu rnyed par dka' //
NK001(ka)035:549: mi dang rab tu 'byung ba dang //
NK001(ka)035:550: tshul khrims phun sum tshogs pa dang //
NK001(ka)035:551: grogs bzang rnyed dka' rnyed gyur nas //
NK001(ka)035:552: mkhas pa dag la legs 'dod cing //
NK001(ka)035:554: sdom brtson rnams kyis so so thar //
NK001(ka)035:555: mnyam pa'i phyir ni 'bad par bgyi //
NK001(ka)035:556: dge slong dbang dul kun dbang po //
NK001(ka)035:557: sangs rgyas mi 'gyur rab byung ba //
NK001(ka)035:558: nges par thar pa 'dod rnams kyis //
NK001(ka)035:559: so sor thar pa rtag tu srungs //
NK001(ka)035:560: bskal pa bye ba rnams su yang //
NK001(ka)035:561: so so thar pa thos pa dang //
NK001(ka)035:562: bzung dang 'dzin pa rnyed dka' ste //
NK001(ka)035:563: sgrub pa'ng shin tu rnyed par dka' //
NK001(ka)035:564: sangs rgyas rnams ni 'byung ba bde //
NK001(ka)035:565: chos bstan pa yang bde ba yin //
NK001(ka)035:566: dge 'dun mthun pa bde ba ste //
NK001(ka)035:567: mthun pa rnams kyi dka' thub bde //
NK001(ka)035:568: 'phags pa rnams ni mthong ba bde //
NK001(ka)035:569: dam pa rnams dang 'grogs pa bde //
NK001(ka)035:570: byis pa rnams ni ma mthong na //
NK001(ka)035:571: rtag tu bde ba nyid du 'gyur //
NK001(ka)035:572: tshul khrims ldan pa mthong ba bde //
NK001(ka)035:573: mang du thos pa mthong ba bde //
NK001(ka)035:574: yang srid rnam par grol ba yi //
NK001(ka)035:575: dgra bcom pa dag mthong ba bde //
NK001(ka)035:576: 'jug ngogs bde ba'i chu klung bde //
NK001(ka)035:577: chos la goms pa'i skye bo bde //
NK001(ka)035:578: shes rab thob par gyur pa bde //
NK001(ka)035:579: nga'o nga rgyal zad pa bde //
NK001(ka)035:580: nges par byas shing dbang po thul ba dag /
NK001(ka)035:581: dgon pa zhi ba rnams su rgas gyur cing //
NK001(ka)035:582: mang du thos pa nags kyi nang dag tu //
NK001(ka)035:583: lang tsho yol ba rnams kyis gnas pa bde //
NK001(ka)035:584: tshe dang ldan pa dag so ka rnams kyi 'das pa dang /
NK001(ka)035:585: lhag ma ji tsam pa de tsam mo //
NK001(ka)035:586: zhes pa'i skabs kyi dus barjoda tshul ni /
NK001(ka)035:587: hor zla bcu pa'i tshes bco lngas ston zla rdzogs pas /
NK001(ka)035:588: de'i phyi nyin tshes bcu drug nas dgun zla dang po shar ba'i phyir /
NK001(ka)035:589: . nas lo 'go 'dzin pa'i dbang du byas nas 'di ltar barjoda par bya ste /
NK001(ka)035:590: hor zla bcu pa'i mar ngo la /
NK001(ka)035:591: tshe dang ldan pa dag sang gi skya rengs shar
NK001(ka)035:592: ba'i tshe dgun stod rnams kyi zla ba phyed ni
NK001(ka)035:593: 'das so // zla ba phyed dang gnyis ni lus so //
NK001(ka)035:594: bcu gcig pa'i yar ngo la /
NK001(ka)035:597: de'i mar ngo la phyed dang gnyis 'das /
NK001(ka)035:599: bcu gnyis pa'i yar ngo la /
NK001(ka)035:600: .gun stod rnams kyi zla ba gnyis 'das te lhag ma ma lus so //
NK001(ka)035:603: .gun smad kyi zla ba gnyis dang /
NK001(ka)035:607: ston zla ba gnyis rnams rigs 'gre shes par bya /
NK001(ka)035:608: gal te zla lhag yod tshe gang lhag pa'i dus
NK001(ka)035:609: tshigs de la bshol dang bcas pa'i zla ba phyed
NK001(ka)035:610: ni 'das so // phyed dang gsum ni lus so //
NK001(ka)035:611: zhes pa lta bu skabs dang bstun te barjoda do //
NK001(ka)035:612: tshe dang ldan pa dag rga ba dang 'chi ba
NK001(ka)035:613: mngon par 'ong zhing ston pa'i bstan pa'ng 'jig par
NK001(ka)035:614: 'gyur bas tshe dang ldan pa dag gis bag yod
NK001(ka)035:616: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi byang chub dang /
NK001(ka)035:617: gzhan yang gang dag de lta bu dang mthun pa'i
NK001(ka)035:618: dge ba'i chos byang chub kyi phyogs rnams kyang bag
NK001(ka)035:620: bcom ldan 'das kyi nyan thos kyi dge 'dun ni don nyung ba bya ba nyung ba yin pas /
NK001(ka)035:621: dge 'dun gyi thog mar bya ba ci yo. /
NK001(ka)035:622: tshe dang ldan pa dag ma lhags pa rnams la 'dun pa dang yongs su dag pa dris shig /
NK001(ka)035:623: dris nas kyang barjoda par bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:624: zhes barjoda ma thag dge bskos kyis brtags pas /
NK001(ka)035:625: mtshams nang gi dge slong na ba sogs rkyen dbang
NK001(ka)035:626: gis 'du ma nus pa yod na 'dun dag len
NK001(ka)035:628: .sa der phyin nas 'dun dag len te /
NK001(ka)035:630: tshe dang ldan pa dgongs su gsol /
NK001(ka)035:631: .nga dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'am bco lnga pa lags la /
NK001(ka)035:634: chos ldan gyi bya bas g.yengs pa ming 'di zhes
NK001(ka)035:635: bgyi ba'i yang gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'am bco lnga
NK001(ka)035:636: pa lags te / bdag dge slong bro 'tshal ba
NK001(ka)035:637: sogs ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i bar chad kyi chos
NK001(ka)035:638: rnams yongs su dag go zhes bdag mchi'o //
NK001(ka)035:639: dge 'dun chos bzhin du mdzad pa la 'dun pa 'bul lo //
NK001(ka)035:640: bdag gi gso sbyong yang yongs su dag go //
NK001(ka)035:641: 'dun pa dang yongs su dag pa yang barjoda do //
NK001(ka)035:642: barjoda pa yang rig par bgyid do //
NK001(ka)035:644: . nas len pa pos nang du 'ongs te dge 'dun la barjoda pa ni /
NK001(ka)035:645: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol /
NK001(ka)035:646: .nga dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'am bco lnga pa lags la /
NK001(ka)035:647: gnas ga ge mo zhig na dge slong bro 'tshal
NK001(ka)035:648: ba sog ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i yang gso sbyong
NK001(ka)035:649: bcu bzhi pa'am bco lnga pa lags te /
NK001(ka)035:650: dge slong bro 'tshal ba sogs ming 'di zhes bgyi
NK001(ka)035:651: ba de bar chad kyi chos rnams yongs su dag
NK001(ka)035:652: go zhes kho na nyid mchi'o //
NK001(ka)035:653: dge 'dun chos bzhin du mdzad pa la 'dun pa 'bul lo //
NK001(ka)035:654: de'i gso sbyong yang yongs su dag go //
NK001(ka)035:655: 'dun pa dang yongs su dag pa yang barjoda do //
NK001(ka)035:656: barjoda pa yang rig par bagyi'o //
NK001(ka)035:659: sh+aakya seng ge de la ni //
NK001(ka)035:660: sor mo bcu yis thal sbyar te //
NK001(ka)035:661: so so thar pa gdon par bya //
NK001(ka)035:662: 'dul ba'i don du nga las nyon ///
NK001(ka)035:663: sa nas drang srong chen po yis //
NK001(ka)035:664: ji skad gsung bzhin bsgrub bya zhing //
NK001(ka)035:665: kha na ma tho phra rnams la //
NK001(ka)035:666: rtun cing byed pa nyid du gyis //
NK001(ka)035:668: sems rta kha blan dka' ba la //
NK001(ka)035:669: mthun pa'i gzer rnon brgya pa yi //
NK001(ka)035:670: srab ni so so thar 'di yin //
NK001(ka)035:671: che ba gang dag ngag tsam gyis //
NK001(ka)035:672: ldog cing mtshams las mi 'da' ba //
NK001(ka)035:673: . dag mi rta bzang po ste //
NK001(ka)035:674: nyon mongs g.yul las nges rgyal 'gyur //
NK001(ka)035:675: su la srab 'di med pa dang //
NK001(ka)035:677: . dag nyon mongs g.yul gyis dkrugs //
NK001(ka)035:679: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol //
NK001(ka)035:680: .nga dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'am bco lnga pa lags te /
NK001(ka)035:681: gal te dge 'dun gyis dus la bab cing bzod na /
NK001(ka)035:682: dge 'dun gyi gnang bar mdzod cig dang /
NK001(ka)035:684: so so thar pa'i mdo gdon pa gdon to //
NK001(ka)035:686: tshe dang ldan pa dag bdag cag gso sbyong bya ste /
NK001(ka)035:687: so so thar pa'i mdo 'don pa gdon gyi /
NK001(ka)035:688: khyed cag su la ltung ba yod pa de mthol zhing /
NK001(ka)035:689: ltung ba med na cang ma smra zhig /
NK001(ka)035:690: cang mi smra na bdag gis tshe- dang ldan pa dag yongs su dag par rig par bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:691: . ltar so sor dris nas dge slong gis lan
NK001(ka)035:692: btab pa de bzhin du dge slong gi 'khor 'di
NK001(ka)035:693: lta bur yang lan gsum gyi bar du bsgrags par
NK001(ka)035:695: yang dge slong gang dge slong gi 'khor 'di lta
NK001(ka)035:696: bur lan gsum gyi bar du bsgrags pa na ltung
NK001(ka)035:697: ba yod la dran bzhin du mi mthol na de
NK001(ka)035:698: shes bzhin du bardzuna du smra ba yin no //
NK001(ka)035:699: tshe dang ldan pa dag shes bzhin du rdzun du
NK001(ka)035:700: smra ba ni bcom ldan 'das kyis bar du gcod
NK001(ka)035:702: . bas na dge slong ltung ba byung ba rnam
NK001(ka)035:703: par dag par 'dod pas ltung ba yod la dran
NK001(ka)035:704: zhing mthong ba mthol bar bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:705: mthol zhing bshags na bde ba la reg par gnas par 'gyur gyi /
NK001(ka)035:706: ma mthol ma bshags na mi 'gyur ro //
NK001(ka)035:707: tshe dang ldan pa dag bdag gis so so thar pa'i mdo 'don pa'i gleng gzhi bton zin to //
NK001(ka)035:708: de la bdag gis tshe dang ldan pa dag la
NK001(ka)035:709: ci 'di la khyed yongs su dag gam zhes dri'o
NK001(ka)035:710: // ci 'di la khyed yongs su dag gam zhes lan gnyis lan gsum du dri'o //
NK001(ka)035:711: 'di la tshe dang ldan pa dag yongs su dag na /
NK001(ka)035:712: 'di ltar cang mi smra ba des de bzhin du 'dzin to //
NK001(ka)035:713: lhag ma thos pa bsgrags pas kyang rung bas 'di skad ces /
NK001(ka)035:715: slad ma pham par 'gyur ba'i chos bzhi dang /
NK001(ka)035:716: dge 'dun lhag ma'i chos bcu gsum dang /
NK001(ka)035:717: ma nges pa'i chos gnyis dang /
NK001(ka)035:718: spang ba ltung byed kyi chos sum cu dang /
NK001(ka)035:719: ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa dgu bcu dang /
NK001(ka)035:720: so sor bshags par bya ba'i chos bzhi dang /
NK001(ka)035:721: bslab par bya ba'i chos mang po dang /
NK001(ka)035:722: rtsod pa zhi bar bya ba'i chos bdun po rnams
NK001(ka)035:723: ni zla ba phyed phyed cing so sor thar pa'i
NK001(ka)035:724: mdo 'don pa las 'byung bas sngar gsan pa'am /
NK001(ka)035:726: zhes mdo'i che ba dang ma lhags pa'i 'dun dag len barjo. /
NK001(ka)035:727: gsol ba dang rnam bzhag 'dzin du gzhug pa sngar
NK001(ka)035:728: bya bas dngos gzhi mdo 'don pa la sngar gsungs
NK001(ka)035:729: pa las / 'dir ding sang gi phyag len ltar gleng gzhi yan rdzogs par bton /
NK001(ka)035:730: . man pham lhag ma nges pa dang ril 'don
NK001(ka)035:731: bzhi po thos pa bsgrags pa'i dbang du byas pa
NK001(ka)035:732: ste / spro zhing nus na ji ltar rigs pa gdon par bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:733: . nas mjug gi bya ba ni /
NK001(ka)035:734: so sor thar pa bton pa yis //
NK001(ka)035:735: bsod nams grub pa gang yod pa //
NK001(ka)035:737: thub dbang go 'phang thob par shog /
NK001(ka)035:738: brtsam par bya zhing dbyung bar bya //
NK001(ka)035:739: sangs rgyas bstan la 'jug par bya //
NK001(ka)035:740: 'dam bu'i khyim la glang chen bzhin //
NK001(ka)035:741: 'chi bdag sde ni gzhom par bya //
NK001(ka)035:742: gang zhig rab tu bag yod pas //
NK001(ka)035:744: skye ba'i 'khor ba rab spangs nas //
NK001(ka)035:745: sdug basngala tha mar byed par 'gyur //
NK001(ka)035:746: phan tshun tshul khrims bsrung ba dang //
NK001(ka)035:747: bstan pa 'phel bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK001(ka)035:748: so sor thar pa 'di bton pas //
NK001(ka)035:749: dge 'dun gyis ni gso sbyong byas //
NK001(ka)035:750: gang gi phyir ni mdo bton dang //
NK001(ka)035:751: gang phyir gso sbyong byas gyur pa'i //
NK001(ka)035:752: tshul khrims 'di ni bsrung bya ste //
NK001(ka)035:753: g.yag rnga'i rtse mo ji bzhin no //
NK001(ka)035:755: gzhan yang bsngo smon dang bkra shis ci rigs pa barjoda par bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:756: gnyis pa dmigs bsal gyi gso sbyong ni /
NK001(ka)035:757: rkyen dbang gis lam du yid kyis byin gyis brlabs pa'am /
NK001(ka)035:758: gnas gcig na rang gcig pu las med na 'dug la /
NK001(ka)035:760: .nga dge 'dun gyi gso sbyong bco lnga pa lags la /
NK001(ka)035:761: bdag dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i yang gso sbyong bco lnga pa lags te /
NK001(ka)035:762: bdag dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba bar chad
NK001(ka)035:763: kyi chos rnams kyis yongs su dag go zhes bdag
NK001(ka)035:764: mchi na bdag yongs su dag par lha rnams kyis
NK001(ka)035:765: bzung du gsol / bdag dge slong ming 'di zhes
NK001(ka)035:766: bgyi ba tshul khrims kyi phung po yongs su rdzogs
NK001(ka)035:768: .nga gso sbyong byin gyis barlaba bo //
NK001(ka)035:769: gang gi tshe dge 'dun tshogs pa rnyed pa de'i
NK001(ka)035:770: tshe dge 'dun dang lhan cig gso sbyong rgya cher
NK001(ka)035:771: nyams su myongs bar bya zhing /
NK001(ka)035:772: so so thar pa'i mdo 'don pa yang gdon par bagyi'o //
NK001(ka)035:773: zhes lan gsum barjoda cing yid la bsam mo //
NK001(ka)035:774: yang dge slong gnyis dang gsum yod na phan tshun gcig gi mdun du gcig 'dug ste /
NK001(ka)035:777: mthar btsun pas bzung du gsol zhes barje zhing thabs legs bya /
NK001(ka)035:779: gso sbyong gi dus la bab pa dang /
NK001(ka)035:780: chos rnams thams cad rgyu las byung //
NK001(ka)035:781: zhes sogs sngon du btang ste /
NK001(ka)035:782: thub pa'i sngon gyi gso sbyong /
NK001(ka)035:783: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK001(ka)035:785: lus kyi sdom pa legs pa ste //
NK001(ka)035:786: ngag gi sdom pa legs pa yin //
NK001(ka)035:787: yid kyi sdom pa legs pa ste //
NK001(ka)035:788: thams cad du ni sdom pa legs //
NK001(ka)035:789: kun tu bsdams pa'i dge slong ni //
NK001(ka)035:790: sdug basngala kun las rab tu grol //
NK001(ka)035:792: . dag ni dus nges pa can gyi gso sbyong ste /
NK001(ka)035:793: gzhan du nges med bkra shis pa'i dang /
NK001(ka)035:795: rtsod pa bzlog pa'i gso sbyong gsum pa la ni /
NK001(ka)035:796: sbyor dngos mjug gsum gyi cho ga thams cad sngar dang 'dra ba las /
NK001(ka)035:797: gsol ba'i las kyi tshe gos sbyong bco lnga pa ste /
NK001(ka)035:799: bkra shis kyi gos sbyong ste /
NK001(ka)035:802: hor zla bcu pa'i tshes bco brgyad lta bu la /
NK001(ka)035:803: .gun stod rnams kyi zla ba dang po'i bar zhag gsum ni 'das so //
NK001(ka)035:804: zla ba gcig dang zhag nyi shu rtsa bdun ni lus so //
NK001(ka)035:805: zhes barjoda pa tsam khyad par ro ////
NK001(ka)035:806: gnyis pa dbyar gyi gzhi'i cho ga la /
NK001(ka)035:808: }na du gtsug lag khang byi dor bya ba dang /
NK001(ka)035:809: rten dgram pa sogs bya zhing /
NK001(ka)035:810: gnas mal gyi gdan spyad sogs stob rgyu yid na sta gon byas la /
NK001(ka)035:812: dbyar zla 'bring po chu stod kyi zla ba rdzogs pa hor zla drug pa'i nya dang /
NK001(ka)035:813: phyi ma yin na dbyar zla tha chung gro zhun
NK001(ka)035:814: gyi zla ba rdzogs pa hor zla bdun pa'i nyi'i
NK001(ka)035:815: nyin par sngar bzhin gso sbyong byas tshar ma thag
NK001(ka)035:816: gnas mal stobs pa'i dge slong gcig gam du ma
NK001(ka)035:818: ji ltar na las byed pas /
NK001(ka)035:819: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba khyo. /
NK001(ka)035:820: dge 'dun la dbyar gyi gnas mal stobs par spro'am /
NK001(ka)035:824: khong spro bar gda' bas gnas mal stob pa bsko-
NK001(ka)035:825: ba la gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las bgyi bas
NK001(ka)035:826: dge 'dun rnams spyod lam bstun nas //
NK001(ka)035:827: ga mar gsol ba'i las la thugs gtad par zhu /
NK001(ka)035:828: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:829: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di dge 'dun la dbyar gyi gnas mal stob par spro na /
NK001(ka)035:830: gal te dge 'dun gyis dus la bab cing bzod na /
NK001(ka)035:831: dge 'dun gyis gnas bar mdzod cig dang /
NK001(ka)035:832: dge 'dun gyis dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba gnas mal stob par bskos te /
NK001(ka)035:833: dge slong gnas mal stob pa ming 'di zhes bgyi
NK001(ka)035:834: ba dge 'dun la dbyar gyi gnas mal stob bo
NK001(ka)035:836: barjoda pa mjug sdud dang bcas pa la thugs gtad par zhu /
NK001(ka)035:838: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di dge 'dun la dbyar gyi gnas mal stob par spro ste /
NK001(ka)035:839: de'i slad du dge 'dun gyis dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba gnas mal stob par bsko na /
NK001(ka)035:840: tshe dang ldan pa gang dag dge slong ming 'di
NK001(ka)035:841: zhes bgyi ba gnas mal stob par bsko bar bzod
NK001(ka)035:842: pa de dag ni cang ma gsung zhig /
NK001(ka)035:843: gang dag mi bzod pa de dag ni gsungs shig /
NK001(ka)035:844: dge 'dun gyis bzod cing gnang nas /
NK001(ka)035:845: dge 'dun gyi dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba gnas mal stob par bskos lags te /
NK001(ka)035:846: 'di ltar cang mi gsung bas de de bzhin du 'dzin to //
NK001(ka)035:848: . ltar bskos pa'i dge slong des gnas mal stobs pa dang tshul shing brim pa yang bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:849: gal te gnas mal stob mi dgos na tshul shing brim pa bsko ba'i cho ga ni /
NK001(ka)035:850: rtsod pa zhi byed nas 'byung ba ltar barjoda de /
NK001(ka)035:852: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba khyod dge 'dun la tshul shing brim par spro'am /
NK001(ka)035:855: }ra gyi dbyar gyi gnas mal stob pa zhes pa'i
NK001(ka)035:856: dod du dge 'dun la tshul shing brim par zhes
NK001(ka)035:857: bsgyur bas gsol gnyis kyi las mjug sdud dang bcas
NK001(ka)035:858: pa barjoda do // .sa tshul shing 'jam zhing drang
NK001(ka)035:859: ba srid du khru gang pa dri bzang pos kha
NK001(ka)035:860: bsgyur ba dge 'dun gyis grangs las mi nyung ba
NK001(ka)035:861: rnams gzeb kyi srog mar ras dkar bting bas dkris
NK001(ka)035:862: pa rgan pa'i mtha' bzhag la /
NK001(ka)035:863: rang nyid 'greng ste thal mo spyar nas dbyar gyi khrims barjoda par bya ste /
NK001(ka)035:864: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:865: bkra shis kyi gtsug lag khang ming 'di zhes bya ba 'di na khrims su bya ba /
NK001(ka)035:866: dge sbyong gi chos bzhi las mi 'da' bar bya ba 'di dang /
NK001(ka)035:867: chos spyod bcu'i bya ba la brtson pas bslab par bya ba 'di dang /
NK001(ka)035:868: dbyar dge 'dun gyi nang du 'khrug long mi bskyed par bya ba 'di dang /
NK001(ka)035:869: ltung ba gleng dran mi bya ba 'di dang /
NK001(ka)035:870: chad pas gcod pa'i las mi bya ba 'di dang /
NK001(ka)035:871: gnas ral ba dang grum pa bcos par bya ba 'di dang /
NK001(ka)035:872: byin gyis ma brlabs par mtshams kyi phyi rol du skya rengs 'char bar mi bya ba 'di dang /
NK001(ka)035:873: dge 'dun gyi spyi gdan la zhabs rjen par mi 'jog pa 'di dang /
NK001(ka)035:874: zhal bshal ba'i chu dge 'dun gyi gtsug lag khang
NK001(ka)035:875: du mi 'dor bar bya ba la sogs pa 'di
NK001(ka)035:876: yod de / khyed cag las gang khrims su bya ba 'di dang 'dis /
NK001(ka)035:877: gnas 'dir gnas par spro ba des ni tshul shing bzhes shig /
NK001(ka)035:878: khyed cag las sus kyang dbyar dge 'dun gyi nang du 'khrug long bskyed par mi bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:879: khyed cag las gang gis 'ga' zhig la cung zad shes pa des smos shig /
NK001(ka)035:880: khyed cag las gang dbyar gyi nang du dge 'dun la 'khrug long bskyed par 'gyur ba de la /
NK001(ka)035:881: dge 'dun gyi phyis nye bar brtag par dgongs so //
NK001(ka)035:882: zhes barjoda nas gral du 'dug go //
NK001(ka)035:884: tshul shing bzhes pa dang dbyar gnas par zhal gyis
NK001(ka)035:885: bzhes pa'i slad du dge 'dun rnams thugs bstun pa
NK001(ka)035:886: gsol ba'i las la thugs gtad par zhu /
NK001(ka)035:887: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:888: .nga dge 'dun gyi dbyar nye bar sgrub pa dbyar
NK001(ka)035:889: zla 'bring po'am tha chung gi tshes bco lnga lags
NK001(ka)035:890: na / gal te dge 'dun gyis dus la bab cing bzod na /
NK001(ka)035:891: dge 'dun gyis gnang bar mdzod cig dang /
NK001(ka)035:892: dge 'dun gyis deng tshul shing bzhes te /
NK001(ka)035:893: sang nang bar dbyar gnas par khas blang ngo //
NK001(ka)035:895: . nas brim pa pos dang por ston pa'i tshul
NK001(ka)035:896: shing dar dang me tog gis dkris pa lag pa'i
NK001(ka)035:897: gung srin gnyis kyis sna gnyis nas blangs te spyi
NK001(ka)035:898: bor reg gnas / 'di ni bdag cag gi ston
NK001(ka)035:899: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas des bzhes
NK001(ka)035:900: bor reg gnas / par mdzad do // zhes barjoda de ston pa'i spyan sngar dbul /
NK001(ka)035:901: . nas sog ma so so'i mdun du khyer te gnas brtan nas rim par brim zhing /
NK001(ka)035:902: len pa po rnams kyis kyang cang mi smra bar
NK001(ka)035:903: stan las phyed 'phags te rang rang gi tshul shing
NK001(ka)035:904: blangs nas dal bus pang du bzhag /
NK001(ka)035:905: dge slong rdzogs pa dang dge tshul rnams kyi tshul shing ni /
NK001(ka)035:907: zhes rang rang gi mkhan slob kyis blang /
NK001(ka)035:908: mjug tu 'di ni gtsug lag khang 'di na gnyug
NK001(ka)035:909: mar gnas pa'i lha'i 'o zhes gnas brtan gyis blang
NK001(ka)035:910: / . nas dge slong dang dge tshul gnyis rim par ma 'dres par bsdus nas grangs bzung ste /
NK001(ka)035:911: brim pa pos 'greng ste thal mo sbyar nas /
NK001(ka)035:912: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:913: bkra shis kyi gtsug lag khang 'di zhes bya ba
NK001(ka)035:914: 'dir dge slong 'di snyed kyis tshul shing bzhes so
NK001(ka)035:916: gral na gnas pa rnams kyis bzhes so zhes lan
NK001(ka)035:917: zer ba dgag dbye'i rigs 'gre las bshad khungs med
NK001(ka)035:919: dge tshul 'di nyid kyis blangs zhes barjoda pa ni
NK001(ka)035:920: mdor ma bshad kyang mchims chen gyi yi ge ltar
NK001(ka)035:922: de'i 'og tu gnas mal stob pa ni /
NK001(ka)035:923: spyir gnas khang dang mal stan sogs gnyug mar gnas
NK001(ka)035:924: pa rnams la bstabs zin pa dag yin mod kyi
NK001(ka)035:925: / 'on kyang glo bur ba la gsar stob dgos pa dang /
NK001(ka)035:926: .ra ma zad stob rgyu yod na so sor stob
NK001(ka)035:927: par bya ba ste bskos pas gnas khang gi sgo
NK001(ka)035:928: lcags dang lde mig bzung nas /
NK001(ka)035:929: dang por gnas brtan gyi mdun du 'dug ste /
NK001(ka)035:930: mkhan po'am slob dpon nam gnas brtan gtsug lag khang
NK001(ka)035:931: 'di ni gos kyi rnyed pa sogs yo byad dang
NK001(ka)035:932: ldan pa lags kyi bzhes shig /
NK001(ka)035:933: ces rgan rim nas dge tshul gyi matha'i bar du'anga
NK001(ka)035:934: rang rang gi gnas khang gi sgo lcags dang lde
NK001(ka)035:935: mig gtad cing / len pa po rnams kyis kyang cang mi smra bar lhung bzed ltar blang ngo //
NK001(ka)035:936: . nas mal stan yang rim pa bzhin du /
NK001(ka)035:937: gdan cha 'di la dbyar tshul dang mthun par longs spyod cig /
NK001(ka)035:938: ces brims tshar ba'i rjes su stob pa pos dge 'dun gyi mthar 'greng ste thal mo sbyar nas /
NK001(ka)035:939: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:940: khyed cag las gang gis kyang dge 'dun gyi gnas
NK001(ka)035:941: mal la gding ba med par longs spyad par mi
NK001(ka)035:942: bya / gding ba rung ba ma yin pas longs spyod par mi bya /
NK001(ka)035:943: gding ba dri ma can gyis longs spyad par mi bya'o //
NK001(ka)035:945: spyod lam de nyid kyis dbyar khas blang ba go bar bya ste /
NK001(ka)035:946: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:948: sbyin bdag 'di zhes bya ba'am dmigs bsal med na
NK001(ka)035:949: skye bo'i tshogs lha dang mi dang klu dang gnod
NK001(ka)035:950: sbyin du bcas pa du ma dang /
NK001(ka)035:951: zhal ta pa 'di zhes bya ba dang /
NK001(ka)035:952: spyod yul gyi grong 'di zhes bya ba dang /
NK001(ka)035:953: bro g.yog pa 'di zhes bya ba'am so sor smos
NK001(ka)035:954: pa 'di rnams la brten te dbyar gnas par zhal
NK001(ka)035:957: . nas bsngo smon dang shis barjoda byas nas grol
NK001(ka)035:958: te dbyar gyi sbyor ba tshul 'jug gi cho ga'o
NK001(ka)035:959: // . nas dbyar khas blang ba dngos gzhi'i cho ga ni /
NK001(ka)035:960: de'i phyi nyin tshes bcu drug gi nang par rang
NK001(ka)035:961: rang so so'i gnas steng g.yogs dang bcas par dge
NK001(ka)035:962: slong gi mdun du khas blang bar bshad kyang /
NK001(ka)035:963: .nga sang 'dus nas mdzad pa phyag len du gda' ba gan+di brdungs te 'dus pa dang /
NK001(ka)035:964: .nga dbyar snga ma zhal gyis bzhes pa'i dus lags te /
NK001(ka)035:965: gtsug lag khang gi bdag po dang /
NK001(ka)035:966: zhes sogs kyis rgyud cha gsum pa dang gzhi bdag la gtor ma btang /
NK001(ka)035:967: . nas dge 'dun du ma longs pa'i dge slong
NK001(ka)035:968: gi mdun du tsog pur 'dug cing thal mo sbyar
NK001(ka)035:969: te / btsun pa dgongs du gsol /
NK001(ka)035:970: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba nang mtshams dang bcas pa'i- gnas 'dir /
NK001(ka)035:971: gnas ral ba dang grum pa bcos pa'i slad du
NK001(ka)035:972: dbyar snga ma zla ba gsum gnas par khas blang
NK001(ka)035:973: ngo // bdag dbyar 'di na mchis shing bdag gi dbyar gyi gnas ni 'di lags so //
NK001(ka)035:974: zhes lan gsum barjoda nas thabs legs bya /
NK001(ka)035:975: dbyar phyi ma yin na dbyar phyi ma zla ba gsum zhes bsgyur /
NK001(ka)035:977: grum pa bcos pa'i slad du zhes pa'i mjug tu /
NK001(ka)035:978: sbyin bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dang /
NK001(ka)035:979: zhal ta ba ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dang /
NK001(ka)035:980: spyod yul gyi grong 'di zhes bgyi ba dang /
NK001(ka)035:981: bro g.yog pa 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK001(ka)035:982: dbyar snga ma zla ba gsum zhes sbyar ro //
